  "subject": "Add ability to use additional nexus repositories",
  "commit_message": "Add ability to use additional nexus repositories\n\nAdd two new properties interval_sec and failure.threshold\nAdd log statements to identify nexus repository\nChange 'upload' boolean to false to prevent upload/delete of files\nOverride 'setResponse()' to prevent caller from receiving error list\n\nIssue-ID: POLICY-2035\nChange-Id: I77e403b3a8e253474793895e1098082cbe02a6ae\nSigned-off-by: Peyton Puckett <peyton.puckett@att.com>\n",
